When responding to this e-mail, 
please include all previous correspondence

ME:
As of July 21, 2002 the problem has been addressed by 2 guides that said
the petition I made would be escalated but is yet to be resolved. The
first failed attempt at the quest was resolved in a manner where I
received the items I turned in to the quest NPC back. The second attempt
to accomplish the goal (receiving the journeyman boots) by turning in
the items that were reimbursed from the first attempt did not work as
well. Hasten B****** (can't remember the exact spelling) responded in
the same manner as the first time and said something along the lines of
"Trade We shall not"

I appreciate the quick response and any effort on resolving this issue.
Thank You 

VI:
Greetings.

Thank you for contacting EverQuest In-Game Customer Support.  
After investigating your situation, it has been determined that we are 
unable to reimburse you.  I understand that such a loss can be 
frustrating, and it is regrettable that we were unable to assist you.


Sincerely,

